        "text": "STANDARD FORM NO. 64\nOffice Memorandum • UNITED STATES GOVERNMENT\nTO MR. LADD\nDATE: March 6, 1950\nFROM A. H. BELMONT\nSUBJECT: UNKNOWN OBJECT OVER OAK RIDGE, TENNESSEE, MARCH 1, 1950;"
